cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.AI 

The paper discusses the simulation of IoT, which involves networking, distributed systems, and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the deployment of smart services in decentralized territories, which involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and system engineering (cs.SY). The use of multi-level simulation involves modeling and analysis (cs.MA), and the paper also discusses the use of ad-hoc wireless networking technologies, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
